Product description

TECLINE JETSTREAM FINS

Classic, rubber, JET - style fins recommended for technical and drysuit divers.

Ergonomic construction of the boot improves comfort for divers with a high instep.
Springy and relatively short blade supports maneuvering in narrow spaces.

SPECIFICATION
- size: XL (42-44)
- material: rubber
- springs: stainless steel + rubber cover
- weight of one fin: 1,80kg
- in-water weight of one fin: 0,51 kg
- color: black
